{"type":"message","id":"a64741ba","parentId":"1e50a8c0","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:23:27.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"เจ้านายบอกให้หาข้อมูลเอง ไม่รู้ว่าอุปกรณ์รุ่นอะไร ผมจะค้นหาวิธีปิด CPU LED RGB แบบทั่วไปก่อน แล้วแบ่งตามยี่ห้อต่างๆ ให้\n","thinkingSignature":"7da5855ccc9673cb746680415ea8dcf73619b27a09b2a787ddc99be6b0297e1d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vihza3arp45n_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"how to turn off CPU LED RGB light multi color software control"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33003,"output":149,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33408,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778199796829,"responseId":"064c5ff87c7e665196a5bdf58d88f50a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7c4ad50","parentId":"a64741ba","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:23:29.267Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vihza3arp45n_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"how to turn off CPU LED RGB light multi color software control\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1126,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a23fb3439eba9e3b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Disable RGB (LED) Lighting on Your Computer\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a23fb3439eba9e3b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.majorgeeks.com/content/page/disable_rgb.html\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"80f354ec06a3d51b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGigabyte RGB Fusion Cooler Master Thermaltake How to Disable RGB Lighting on Your Computer - Motherboard Some computers, for example, the Hewlett Packard Envy and Omen series, have RGB lighting for the logo and the inside of the tower. Unlike most RGB lighting, you can often disable this light by removing the power from the pins on the motherboard.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"80f354ec06a3d51b\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.majorgeeks.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"73b478ec4d50a430\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to turn off RGB on a Windows 11/10 PC - The Windows Club\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"73b478ec4d50a430\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thewindowsclub.com/how-to-turn-off-rgb-on-a-windows-11-10-pc\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c232e827385d4c84\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIs RGB causing too much light on your PC? To turn off RGB or customize it to be less distracting, configure the BIOS or use OpenRGB Software .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c232e827385d4c84\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.thewindowsclub.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"38e2fba64748ad44\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Turn Off RGB Lights on PC Windows 11: Total Control Guide\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"38e2fba64748ad44\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://techradar.info/how-to-turn-off-rgb-lights-on-pc-windows-11-total-control-guide/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"700f84c3b1eae19f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nImpact of Disabling RGB on System Performance Beyond aesthetics, turning off RGB lights on PC Windows 11 can have minor technical benefits. LED controllers and the software required to run them consume CPU cycles and system memory. In extreme cases, poorly optimized RGB software can cause \\\"micro-stuttering\\\" in high-performance gaming scenarios.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"700f84c3b1eae19f\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"techradar.info\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"86000c92de4ae677\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenRGB\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"86000c92de4ae677\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openrgb.org/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"177d5af6b7ce6290\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nControl RGB without wasting system resources Lightweight User Interface OpenRGB keeps it simple with a lightweight user interface that doesn't waste background resources with excessive custom images and styles. It is light on both RAM and CPU usage, so your system can continue to shine without cutting into your gaming or productivity performance.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"177d5af6b7ce6290\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openrgb.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a61ee3a7b2d282c4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPC RGB Too Bright at Night? Turn Off LED Lights Fast\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a61ee3a7b2d282c4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.coohom.com/article/how-to-turn-off-led-lights-on-your-pc\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c81e093da14c68cf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nLearn how to turn off PC LED lights using motherboard apps, BIOS settings, fan controllers, and peripheral software .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c81e093da14c68cf\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.coohom.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"how to turn off CPU LED RGB light multi color software control","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":1126,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a23fb3439eba9e3b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to Disable RGB (LED) Lighting on Your Computer\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a23fb3439eba9e3b\">>>","url":"https://www.majorgeeks.com/content/page/disable_rgb.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"80f354ec06a3d51b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGigabyte RGB Fusion Cooler Master Thermaltake How to Disable RGB Lighting on Your Computer - Motherboard Some computers, for example, the Hewlett Packard Envy and Omen series, have RGB lighting for the logo and the inside of the tower. Unlike most RGB lighting, you can often disable this light by removing the power from the pins on the motherboard.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"80f354ec06a3d51b\">>>","siteName":"www.majorgeeks.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"73b478ec4d50a430\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to turn off RGB on a Windows 11/10 PC - The Windows Club\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"73b478ec4d50a430\">>>","url":"https://www.thewindowsclub.com/how-to-turn-off-rgb-on-a-windows-11-10-pc","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c232e827385d4c84\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIs RGB causing too much light on your PC? To turn off RGB or customize it to be less distracting, configure the BIOS or use OpenRGB Software .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c232e827385d4c84\">>>","siteName":"www.thewindowsclub.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"38e2fba64748ad44\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to Turn Off RGB Lights on PC Windows 11: Total Control Guide\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"38e2fba64748ad44\">>>","url":"https://techradar.info/how-to-turn-off-rgb-lights-on-pc-windows-11-total-control-guide/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"700f84c3b1eae19f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nImpact of Disabling RGB on System Performance Beyond aesthetics, turning off RGB lights on PC Windows 11 can have minor technical benefits. LED controllers and the software required to run them consume CPU cycles and system memory. In extreme cases, poorly optimized RGB software can cause \"micro-stuttering\" in high-performance gaming scenarios.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"700f84c3b1eae19f\">>>","siteName":"techradar.info"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"86000c92de4ae677\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenRGB\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"86000c92de4ae677\">>>","url":"https://openrgb.org/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"177d5af6b7ce6290\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nControl RGB without wasting system resources Lightweight User Interface OpenRGB keeps it simple with a lightweight user interface that doesn't waste background resources with excessive custom images and styles. It is light on both RAM and CPU usage, so your system can continue to shine without cutting into your gaming or productivity performance.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"177d5af6b7ce6290\">>>","siteName":"openrgb.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a61ee3a7b2d282c4\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPC RGB Too Bright at Night? Turn Off LED Lights Fast\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a61ee3a7b2d282c4\">>>","url":"https://www.coohom.com/article/how-to-turn-off-led-lights-on-your-pc","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c81e093da14c68cf\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nLearn how to turn off PC LED lights using motherboard apps, BIOS settings, fan controllers, and peripheral software .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c81e093da14c68cf\">>>","siteName":"www.coohom.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778199809266}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ab3f1f3","parentId":"a7c4ad50","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:23:34.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for more specific info about BIOS settings and software options.\n","thinkingSignature":"efd037a50b261ebeebd578dfbb4745af262d413aaddb205e50a9c4963661a010"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_onofouw3bjwt_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"how to disable RGB LED BIOS settings motherboard without software"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1299,"output":49,"cacheRead":33216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34564,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778199809268,"responseId":"064c600210b2a9e34f1e9c3c10ad34a4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cd7324a","parentId":"3ab3f1f3","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:23:35.429Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_onofouw3bjwt_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"how to disable RGB LED BIOS settings motherboard without software\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 863,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a290a0b88c077ff\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCan I turn off all the LED lights on the motherboard in BIOS?\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a290a0b88c077ff\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.msi.com/faq/3532\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d22b0ecdfbce38f4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnswer You could enter BIOS setup and disable RGB Light Control and Indication LED Control, press F10 to Save & Exit, by doing this you could turn off all the LEDs on the motherboard except for EZ Debug LEDs .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d22b0ecdfbce38f4\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.msi.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0ca3eb443b0ace22\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe Ultimate Guide to Disabling RGB Lights on PC Fans Without Extra ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0ca3eb443b0ace22\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://smart.dhgate.com/the-ultimate-guide-to-disabling-rgb-lights-on-pc-fans-without-extra-software/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b1f9b36130b8a75c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nUse your motherboard BIOS settings : Believe it or not, some BIOS interfaces let you disable RGB lighting without Windows software . Dive into your BIOS menu, search for onboard LED or lighting settings , and toggle those off.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b1f9b36130b8a75c\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"smart.dhgate.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"be381964c320cc67\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Disable RGB (LED) Lighting on Your Computer\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"be381964c320cc67\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.majorgeeks.com/content/page/disable_rgb.html\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea9b208e54388546\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nYou should be able to locate your motherboard manual online to find what pins power your RGB lighting. How to Disable RGB Lighting on Your Computer - BIOS The BIOS , much like the motherboard , is best used if you have some experience. This is because every BIOS is different, so the settings for RGB will be different for every brand motherboard .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea9b208e54388546\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.majorgeeks.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5ae3469038ea3599\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to turn off RGB on a Windows 11/10 PC - The Windows Club\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5ae3469038ea3599\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thewindowsclub.com/how-to-turn-off-rgb-on-a-windows-11-10-pc\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8b0a65f93c66dcac\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIs RGB causing too much light on your PC? To turn off RGB or customize it to be less distracting, configure the BIOS or use OpenRGB Software .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8b0a65f93c66dcac\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.thewindowsclub.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"82153b98257b9a6a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow do I disable RGB in MSI BIOS? - YouTube\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"82153b98257b9a6a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3y0zZFYb36I\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"67d323420c12cfa6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDisabling RGB in MSI BIOS : A Step-by-Step Guide 👉 MSI RGB Disable 👉 Learn how to easily turn off RGB lighting in MSI BIOS with this simple step-by-step guide.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"67d323420c12cfa6\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.youtube.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"how to disable RGB LED BIOS settings motherboard without software","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":863,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1a290a0b88c077ff\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCan I turn off all the LED lights on the motherboard in BIOS?\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1a290a0b88c077ff\">>>","url":"https://www.msi.com/faq/3532","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d22b0ecdfbce38f4\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAnswer You could enter BIOS setup and disable RGB Light Control and Indication LED Control, press F10 to Save & Exit, by doing this you could turn off all the LEDs on the motherboard except for EZ Debug LEDs .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d22b0ecdfbce38f4\">>>","siteName":"www.msi.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0ca3eb443b0ace22\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe Ultimate Guide to Disabling RGB Lights on PC Fans Without Extra ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0ca3eb443b0ace22\">>>","url":"https://smart.dhgate.com/the-ultimate-guide-to-disabling-rgb-lights-on-pc-fans-without-extra-software/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b1f9b36130b8a75c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nUse your motherboard BIOS settings : Believe it or not, some BIOS interfaces let you disable RGB lighting without Windows software . Dive into your BIOS menu, search for onboard LED or lighting settings , and toggle those off.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b1f9b36130b8a75c\">>>","siteName":"smart.dhgate.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"be381964c320cc67\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to Disable RGB (LED) Lighting on Your Computer\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"be381964c320cc67\">>>","url":"https://www.majorgeeks.com/content/page/disable_rgb.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ea9b208e54388546\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nYou should be able to locate your motherboard manual online to find what pins power your RGB lighting. How to Disable RGB Lighting on Your Computer - BIOS The BIOS , much like the motherboard , is best used if you have some experience. This is because every BIOS is different, so the settings for RGB will be different for every brand motherboard .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ea9b208e54388546\">>>","siteName":"www.majorgeeks.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5ae3469038ea3599\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to turn off RGB on a Windows 11/10 PC - The Windows Club\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5ae3469038ea3599\">>>","url":"https://www.thewindowsclub.com/how-to-turn-off-rgb-on-a-windows-11-10-pc","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8b0a65f93c66dcac\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIs RGB causing too much light on your PC? To turn off RGB or customize it to be less distracting, configure the BIOS or use OpenRGB Software .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8b0a65f93c66dcac\">>>","siteName":"www.thewindowsclub.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"82153b98257b9a6a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow do I disable RGB in MSI BIOS? - YouTube\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"82153b98257b9a6a\">>>","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3y0zZFYb36I","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"67d323420c12cfa6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDisabling RGB in MSI BIOS : A Step-by-Step Guide 👉 MSI RGB Disable 👉 Learn how to easily turn off RGB lighting in MSI BIOS with this simple step-by-step guide.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"67d323420c12cfa6\">>>","siteName":"www.youtube.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778199815429}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc6b8e9c","parentId":"1cd7324a","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:23:58.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me give the boss a comprehensive answer about how to turn off RGB LED lights. Based on the search results, there are several approaches:\n\n1. BIOS/UEFI settings - most reliable\n2. Manufacturer software (like ASUS Aura, MSI Center, etc.)\n3. OpenRGB - universal third-party tool\n\nLet me summarize these options clearly in Thai.\n","thinkingSignature":"0c5958ae252e62b5b846c358918189701048e4e0e0147fa08f05b596ee0616f5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 มี **3 ทาง** ปิดไฟ RGB LED ใน PC ครับ:\n\n---\n\n## 1️⃣ ปิดจาก BIOS (วิธีที่ดีที่สุด ไม่ต้องติดตั้งซอฟต์แวร์)\n\nเข้า BIOS ตอนเปิดเครื่อง (กด `Del` หรือ `F2` ขึ้นกับแต่ละยี่ห้อ)\n\nหาเมนูประมาณนี้:\n- **MSI** → `Settings → Advanced → RGB Light Control` → ปิด\n- **ASUS** → `AI Suite / BIOS → Advanced → Q-Fan Control / RGB`\n- **Gigabyte** → `BIOS → Settings → RGB Fusion`\n- **ASRock** → `BIOS → Tools → RGB LED`\n\n> ⚠️ ถ้าไม่รู้ยี่ห้อเมนบอร์ด เข้า BIOS ก่อนแล้วถ่ายรูปหน้าจอมาให้ผมดูได้ครับ\n\n---\n\n## 2️⃣ ใช้ OpenRGB (ฟรี, รองรับหลายยี่ห้อ)\n\nดาวน์โหลดที่ → **openrgb.org**\n\n- ไม่ต้องติดตั้งซอฟต์แวร์ยี่ห้อ (ประหยัด RAM/CPU)\n- รองรับ: Corsair, NZXT, ASUS, MSI, Gigabyte, Cooler Master ฯลฯ\n- เปิดมา → ปิดไฟทุกอัน → Apply\n\n---\n\n## 3️⃣ ปิดด้วยซอฟต์แวร์ของยี่ห้อนั้นๆ\n\n| ยี่ห้อ | ซอฟต์แวร์ |\n|--------|-----------|\n| ASUS | Armoury Crate / Aura Creator |\n| MSI | MSI Center / Dragon Center |\n| Gigabyte | RGB Fusion 2.0 |\n| Corsair | iCUE |\n| NZXT | CAM / NZXT CAM |\n| Cooler Master | MasterPlus+ |\n\n---\n\n**แนะนำ:** ลองเข้า **BIOS ก่อน** เพราะปิดได้เลยไม่ต้องติดตั้งอะไรเพิ่ม แจ้งยี่ห้อเมนบอร์ด/คูลเลอร์มาได้ถ้าต้องการทางเจาะจงกว่านี้ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1263,"output":779,"cacheRead":34496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36538,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778199815430,"responseId":"064c6009914c62051274e00e18ad636d"}}
