{"type":"message","id":"6496d89a","parentId":"9a4a478e","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:27:14.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"ปิดหน้าจอคอม\" which means \"turn off the computer screen\". They want to turn off their monitor/screen.\n","thinkingSignature":"6dce7c0d0a5134ad298600b198e8a3742e9dcb9cd04b796a4e94d4ebbaa3028b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 วิธีปิดหน้าจอคอมชั่วคราว:\n\n**Windows:**\n- กด `Win + D` แล้วลองกด `Win + L` (ล็อกหน้าจอ)\n- หรือ ปิดจอไปเลย → `Win + X` → `U` → `S` (Sleep)\n\n**จอปิดเอง:**\n- ไปที่ `Settings → System → Power → Screen off timeout` → ตั้งเวลาสั้นๆ\n\n**ถ้าต้องการปิดจอทันที:**\n```\nWin + D → Alt + F4 → Enter (ปิดเครื่อง)\n```\nหรือกดปุ่มเปิด-ปิดจอที่หน้าจอโดยตรงเลยก็ได้ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3397,"output":289,"cacheRead":33088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778200023261,"responseId":"064c60d970305d59ca4086f6db9f3dc3"}}
