{"type":"message","id":"18d06b3e","parentId":"7f73dece","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:28:44.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to turn off the computer screen completely. They want me to actually do it for them, not just give instructions. I can do this via exec command on their Windows machine through WSL.\n\nLet me use a command to turn off the monitor. On Windows, you can use:\n- `powershell (Add-Type '[DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")]^[void]::SendMessage((Get-Process -id $p).MainWindowHandle,0x0112,0xF170,2)'` - but this is complex\n- Simpler: use ` NirCmd` or PowerShell to turn off monitor\n\nThe simplest command via WSL/cmd would be:\n```\npowershell -Command \"(Add-Type '[DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")]public static extern int SendMessage(int hWnd,int hMsg,int wParam,int lParam);')[DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")]::SendMessage(0xffff,0x0112,0xF170,2)\"\n```\n\nOr on Windows directly, you can press `Win + X` then `U` then `I` which is the shortcut for \"Shut down or sign out → Sleep\" but turning off the monitor completely is different from sleep.\n\nActually the most direct way to turn OFF the monitor (not sleep, but actually power it down) on Windows is to use the Windows key + L to lock, and then wait for the display to turn off via timeout, OR use:\n\n```\npowercfg /change monitor-timeout-ac 0\n```\n\nBut I think what the user wants is the simplest way to turn off the monitor immediately. Let me send the command via exec.\n","thinkingSignature":"eca093b09847d7066efe472653ce04a864dec12af32ee17cffb4d3f4f359fc2c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cb6gpzim9i48_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"& {(Add-Type -TypeDefinition '[DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")]public static extern int SendMessage(int hWnd,int hMsg,int wParam,int lParam);' -Passthru)::SendMessage(0xffff,0x0112,0xF170,-1)}\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":467,"output":437,"cacheRead":36288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778200106500,"responseId":"064c612d2a955202c3d2b187190949b6"}}
