{"type":"message","id":"4f3a039f","parentId":"20e811d2","timestamp":"2026-05-08T06:21:27.357Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I don't see a systemInstruction in the openclaw.json config at all. Let me check if OpenClaw has a different way to set system instructions - maybe through the agents config or through the identity files.\n\nLet me look for a systemInstruction in the entire OpenClaw config structure or check if there's a separate config file.\n\nActually, looking at the question again - the user asked me to look at `~/.openclaw/config.yaml` specifically. But that file doesn't exist. Maybe it's `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` that acts as the config, and there might be a systemInstruction somewhere in it.\n\nWait - looking at my startup context, there are injected \"Project Context\" files. \n\nThe systemInstruction might be injected at runtime by OpenClaw rather than stored as a file. Looking at the files I have access to - SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, USER.md, MEMORY.md - none of these contain the specific \"systemInstruction\" field the user mentioned. Let me check if there's a systemInstruction in OpenClaw's agent configuration or identity settings that I might have missed.\n\nThe user mentioned comparing three sources but config.yaml doesn't seem to exist, so I should check OpenClaw's documentation to understand how system instructions are actually configured in this system.\n","thinkingSignature":"6fb3ab2143920ed6cdb50f7611f123395dba1acf41fc66b986f5bd624a785df8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ft2nf4ytg645_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/agents/ 2>/dev/null && cat ~/.openclaw/agents/*.yaml 2>/dev/null || cat ~/.openclaw/agents/*.json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ft2nf4ytg645_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"systemInstruction\" ~/.openclaw/ 2>/dev/null | head -20","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":558,"output":384,"cacheRead":51520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52462,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778221271075,"responseId":"064cb3d92df62f9ed3ec53f5feb2b344"}}
