{"type":"message","id":"f2bcbb4b","parentId":"362b1f39","timestamp":"2026-05-08T09:34:27.787Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_h9r7b86e6mah_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"AiFace — ChatGPT Custom GPT image generator for human faces.\n\nControls Chrome through CDP/Playwright only: no OS mouse movement, no real keyboard,\nno UFO clicking. Designed for the user's logged-in Windows Chrome profile.\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport asyncio\nimport base64\nimport json\nimport os\nimport re\nimport shutil\nimport sys\nimport time\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional, Tuple\n\nfrom playwright.async_api import async_playwright, TimeoutError as PlaywrightTimeoutError\n\nGPT_URL = \"https://chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9\"\nDEFAULT_CDP = \"http://127.0.0.1:9223\"\nDEFAULT_OUT_DIR = r\"C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป AiFace\" if os.name == \"nt\" else \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/รูป AiFace\"\nDEFAULT_RUNTIME_DIR = r\"C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-aiface\\runtime 🏃💨\" if os.name == \"nt\" else \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/ufo-aiface/runtime 🏃💨\"\nDEFAULT_OLLAMA_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:11434\"\nDEFAULT_VISION_MODEL = \"moondream:latest\"\nDEFAULT_TEXT_JUDGE_MODEL = \"qwen2.5:3b\"\n\n\ndef safe_name(text: str, max_len: int = 36) -> str:\n    text = re.sub(r\"[^0-9A-Za-zก-๙_-]+\", \"_\", text).strip(\"_\")\n    return (text[:max_len] or \"aiface_image\")\n\n\ndef reset_runtime_dir() -> Path:\n    runtime_dir = Path(DEFAULT_RUNTIME_DIR)\n    if runtime_dir.exists():\n        shutil.rmtree(runtime_dir, ignore_errors=True)\n    runtime_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    return runtime_dir\n\n\ndef cleanup_runtime_dir(runtime_dir: Optional[Path]):\n    if not runtime_dir:\n        return\n    try:\n        if runtime_dir.exists():\n            shutil.rmtree(runtime_dir, ignore_errors=True)\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n\n\nasync def find_or_create_gpt_page(context):\n    for pg in context.pages:\n        if \"chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9\" in (pg.url or \"\"):\n            return pg\n    pg = await context.new_page()\n    await pg.goto(GPT_URL, wait_until=\"domcontentloaded\", timeout=60000)\n    return pg\n\n\nasync def set_prompt_without_real_keyboard(page, prompt: str):\n    box = page.locator(\"#prompt-textarea\").last\n    await box.wait_for(state=\"visible\", timeout=30000)\n\n    await box.evaluate(\n        \"\"\"(el, text) => {\n            el.focus();\n            if (el.tagName === 'TEXTAREA' || el.tagName === 'INPUT') {\n                el.value = text;\n            } else {\n                el.textContent = text;\n            }\n            el.dispatchEvent(new InputEvent('input', {bubbles: true, inputType: 'insertText', data: text}));\n            el.dispatchEvent(new Event('change', {bubbles: true}));\n        }\"\"\",\n        prompt,\n    )\n\n    send_candidates = [\n        \"button[data-testid='send-button']\",\n        \"button[aria-label*='Send']\",\n        \"button[aria-label*='ส่ง']\",\n    ]\n    for sel in send_candidates:\n        btn = page.locator(sel).last\n        try:\n            if await btn.count() and await btn.is_enabled(timeout=1500):\n                await btn.click(timeout=5000)\n                return\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n    await box.press(\"Enter\")\n\n\nasync def collect_large_images(page):"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"AiFace — ChatGPT Custom GPT image generator for human faces.\n\nControls Chrome through CDP/Playwright only: no OS mouse movement, no real keyboard,\nno UFO clicking. Designed for the user's logged-in Windows Chrome profile.\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport asyncio\nimport base64\nimport json\nimport os\nimport re\nimport shutil\nimport sys\nimport time\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional, Tuple\n\nfrom playwright.async_api import async_playwright, TimeoutError as PlaywrightTimeoutError\n\nGPT_URL = \"https://chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9\"\nDEFAULT_CDP = \"http://127.0.0.1:9223\"\nDEFAULT_OUT_DIR = r\"C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป AiFace\" if os.name == \"nt\" else \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/รูป AiFace\"\nDEFAULT_RUNTIME_DIR = r\"C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-aiface\\runtime 🏃💨\" if os.name == \"nt\" else \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/ufo-aiface/runtime 🏃💨\"\nDEFAULT_OLLAMA_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:11434\"\nDEFAULT_VISION_MODEL = \"moondream:latest\"\nDEFAULT_TEXT_JUDGE_MODEL = \"qwen2.5:3b\"\n\n\ndef safe_name(text: str, max_len: int = 36) -> str:\n    text = re.sub(r\"[^0-9A-Za-zก-๙_-]+\", \"_\", text).strip(\"_\")\n    return (text[:max_len] or \"aiface_image\")\n\n\ndef reset_runtime_dir() -> Path:\n    runtime_dir = Path(DEFAULT_RUNTIME_DIR)\n    if runtime_dir.exists():\n        shutil.rmtree(runtime_dir, ignore_errors=True)\n    runtime_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    return runtime_dir\n\n\ndef cleanup_runtime_dir(runtime_dir: Optional[Path]):\n    if not runtime_dir:\n        return\n    try:\n        if runtime_dir.exists():\n            shutil.rmtree(runtime_dir, ignore_errors=True)\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n\n\nasync def find_or_create_gpt_page(context):\n    for pg in context.pages:\n        if \"chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9\" in (pg.url or \"\"):\n            return pg\n    pg = await context.new_page()\n    await pg.goto(GPT_URL, wait_until=\"domcontentloaded\", timeout=60000)\n    return pg\n\n\nasync def set_prompt_without_real_keyboard(page, prompt: str):\n    box = page.locator(\"#prompt-textarea\").last\n    await box.wait_for(state=\"visible\", timeout=30000)\n\n    await box.evaluate(\n        \"\"\"(el, text) => {\n            el.focus();\n            if (el.tagName === 'TEXTAREA' || el.tagName === 'INPUT') {\n                el.value = text;\n            } else {\n                el.textContent = text;\n            }\n            el.dispatchEvent(new InputEvent('input', {bubbles: true, inputType: 'insertText', data: text}));\n            el.dispatchEvent(new Event('change', {bubbles: true}));\n        }\"\"\",\n        prompt,\n    )\n\n    send_candidates = [\n        \"button[data-testid='send-button']\",\n        \"button[aria-label*='Send']\",\n        \"button[aria-label*='ส่ง']\",\n    ]\n    for sel in send_candidates:\n        btn = page.locator(sel).last\n        try:\n            if await btn.count() and await btn.is_enabled(timeout=1500):\n                await btn.click(timeout=5000)\n                return\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n    await box.press(\"Enter\")\n\n\nasync def collect_large_images(page):","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778232867786}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdf10bb6","parentId":"f2bcbb4b","timestamp":"2026-05-08T09:34:27.787Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_h9r7b86e6mah_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: ufo-gpt-image-gen\ndescription: |\n  Generate 3D prop/object images via ChatGPT Custom GPT using Chrome CDP automation.\n  Use when boss wants to create images for 3D modeling workflow.\n  Triggers: boss asks to generate an image, provides a Thai prompt for a prop/object,\n  using ChatGPT to create images for 3D printing/modeling, or any image generation request\n  that uses the Custom GPT at chatgpt.com/g/g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1.\n  This skill replaces manual ChatGPT Web usage — it runs gpt_background_image.py which\n  handles Chrome CDP connection, prompt submission via DOM, dual verification gates\n  (technical + Moondream vision), and auto-cleanup.\n---\n\n# ufo-gpt-image-gen\n\nGenerate images via ChatGPT Custom GPT for 3D modeling using Chrome CDP automation.\n\n## Quick Usage\n\n```bash\nbash \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/ufo-gpt-image-gen/generate_bg.sh\" \"ร้านขายผ้าสีสันสดใส\"\n```\n\nOutput: PNG saved to `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป 3D\\`\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. **Start Chrome CDP** via `start_chrome_bg.ps1` (verifies port 9222 is listening)\n2. **Run `gpt_background_image.py`** — connects Chrome, submits prompt via DOM, waits for generated image\n3. **Technical Gate** — image URL must be `backend-api/estuary/content`, resolution >= 1000x700, size >= 300KB\n4. **Vision Gate** — Moondream describes image, qwen2.5:3b judges match (confidence >= 0.75)\n5. **Save & cleanup** — PNG to output folder, delete `runtime 🏃💨` temp folder\n\n## Key Paths\n\n| Purpose | Windows Path |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Output folder** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป 3D\\` |\n| **Tool root** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-gpt-image-gen\\` |\n| **Runtime temp** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-gpt-image-gen\\runtime 🏃💨\\` |\n| **Chrome CDP** | `http://[::1]:9222` |\n| **GPT URL** | `https://chatgpt.com/g/g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1` |\n\n## Scripts\n\n| Script | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `generate_bg.sh` | Main entry — call from WSL/Linux |\n| `start_chrome_bg.ps1` | Start/verify Chrome remote debugging |\n| `gpt_background_image.py` | Core automation (CDP connect → DOM input → verify → save) |\n| `verify_image_moondream.py` | Single image verification tool |\n\n## Verification Gates\n\nSee [references/verification.md](references/verification.md) for full details.\n\n## Notes\n\n- No real keyboard/mouse — all via CDP/DOM only\n- Runtime temp folder is auto-deleted after completion\n- Rejects thumbnails, previews, avatars automatically\n- Only ChatGPT estuary content URLs are accepted"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"---\nname: ufo-gpt-image-gen\ndescription: |\n  Generate 3D prop/object images via ChatGPT Custom GPT using Chrome CDP automation.\n  Use when boss wants to create images for 3D modeling workflow.\n  Triggers: boss asks to generate an image, provides a Thai prompt for a prop/object,\n  using ChatGPT to create images for 3D printing/modeling, or any image generation request\n  that uses the Custom GPT at chatgpt.com/g/g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1.\n  This skill replaces manual ChatGPT Web usage — it runs gpt_background_image.py which\n  handles Chrome CDP connection, prompt submission via DOM, dual verification gates\n  (technical + Moondream vision), and auto-cleanup.\n---\n\n# ufo-gpt-image-gen\n\nGenerate images via ChatGPT Custom GPT for 3D modeling using Chrome CDP automation.\n\n## Quick Usage\n\n```bash\nbash \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/ufo-gpt-image-gen/generate_bg.sh\" \"ร้านขายผ้าสีสันสดใส\"\n```\n\nOutput: PNG saved to `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป 3D\\`\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. **Start Chrome CDP** via `start_chrome_bg.ps1` (verifies port 9222 is listening)\n2. **Run `gpt_background_image.py`** — connects Chrome, submits prompt via DOM, waits for generated image\n3. **Technical Gate** — image URL must be `backend-api/estuary/content`, resolution >= 1000x700, size >= 300KB\n4. **Vision Gate** — Moondream describes image, qwen2.5:3b judges match (confidence >= 0.75)\n5. **Save & cleanup** — PNG to output folder, delete `runtime 🏃💨` temp folder\n\n## Key Paths\n\n| Purpose | Windows Path |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Output folder** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป 3D\\` |\n| **Tool root** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-gpt-image-gen\\` |\n| **Runtime temp** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-gpt-image-gen\\runtime 🏃💨\\` |\n| **Chrome CDP** | `http://[::1]:9222` |\n| **GPT URL** | `https://chatgpt.com/g/g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1` |\n\n## Scripts\n\n| Script | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `generate_bg.sh` | Main entry — call from WSL/Linux |\n| `start_chrome_bg.ps1` | Start/verify Chrome remote debugging |\n| `gpt_background_image.py` | Core automation (CDP connect → DOM input → verify → save) |\n| `verify_image_moondream.py` | Single image verification tool |\n\n## Verification Gates\n\nSee [references/verification.md](references/verification.md) for full details.\n\n## Notes\n\n- No real keyboard/mouse — all via CDP/DOM only\n- Runtime temp folder is auto-deleted after completion\n- Rejects thumbnails, previews, avatars automatically\n- Only ChatGPT estuary content URLs are accepted","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778232867786}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0a3b58d","parentId":"fdf10bb6","timestamp":"2026-05-08T09:35:40.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! The \"aiface\" on the computer is actually two different things:\n\n1. `ufo-aiface` folder - contains `gpt_aiface_image.py` which is for generating human faces via a DIFFERENT ChatGPT Custom GPT: `g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9`\n2. `รูป AiFace` folder - output folder for face images\n\nThe user wants me to read the skill for aiface. But there's no \"aiface\" skill in OpenClaw's plugin-skills. However, the ufo-aiface folder contains the `gpt_aiface_image.py` script which IS the aiface tool - it just uses a different ChatGPT GPT URL for faces.\n\n\nI should walk the user through what I'm seeing and ask them to clarify what they'd like me to do with this setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"78a7b387287fa87a4950720eec5e458d22403b65a9952d8210b36b530868c189"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 เจอแล้วครับ! **AiFace อยู่ที่เครื่อง Windows:**\n\n**Folder:** `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-aiface\\`\n\n**ไฟล์หลัก:**\n- `gpt_aiface_image.py` — สคริปต์หลักสำหรับสร้างรูปหน้าคนผ่าน ChatGPT Custom GPT เฉพาะ\n- **GPT URL:** `https://chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9` (ต่างจาก ufo-gpt-image-gen ที่ใช้ `g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1`)\n\n**Output folder:** `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป AiFace\\` (มีรูป Kriang หลายเวอร์ชัน)\n\n---\n\n**สิ่งที่ยังไม่มีใน OpenClaw:**\n❌ ไม่มี `ufo-aiface` skill ใน `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/` — มีแค่ `ufo-gpt-image-gen` (สำหรับ prop/object 3D)\n\nเจ้านายอยากให้ผมสร้าง skill `ufo-aiface` ให้ OpenClaw เลยไหมครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1752,"output":570,"cacheRead":94848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778232867789,"responseId":"064ce1259746f1cd4fbc9eb0197