{"type":"message","id":"45a3ceb0","parentId":"d17ad624","timestamp":"2026-05-08T09:39:08.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the SKILL.md and supporting scripts.\n","thinkingSignature":"baae3bb6132748778b7f8b81a1d4f387daf0b909d6ea94eb6090df3f13c54406"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kqap5xe16jef_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: ufo-aiface\ndescription: |\n  Generate realistic human face portraits via ChatGPT Custom GPT (AiFace) using Chrome CDP automation.\n  Use when boss wants to create face images for 3D modeling workflow.\n  Triggers: boss asks to generate a face, provides a Thai prompt for a character/person,\n  using ChatGPT to create human face images, or any image generation request that\n  uses the Custom GPT at chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9.\n  This skill replaces manual ChatGPT Web usage — it runs gpt_aiface_image.py which\n  handles Chrome CDP connection, prompt submission via DOM, dual verification gates\n  (technical + Moondream vision), and auto-cleanup.\n---\n\n# ufo-aiface\n\nGenerate human face images via ChatGPT Custom GPT for AiFace using Chrome CDP automation.\n\n## Quick Usage\n\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-aiface/run_aiface.sh \"ไอ้เกรียง ถูกชายกำนันคง หน้าผู้ร้ายไทย อายุ 40 ผมเกลี้ยง โอน นามแฝง คอพัง กางเกงลาย ฮู้หยักสี\"\n```\n\nOutput: PNG saved to `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป AiFace\\`\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. **Start Chrome CDP** via `launch_chrome.ps1` (verifies port 9223 is listening)\n2. **Run `gpt_aiface_image.py`** — connects Chrome, submits prompt via DOM, waits for generated image\n3. **Technical Gate** — image URL must be `backend-api/estuary/content`, resolution >= 1000x700, size >= 300KB\n4. **Vision Gate** — Moondream describes image, qwen2.5:3b judges match (confidence >= 0.75)\n5. **Save & cleanup** — PNG to output folder, delete `runtime 🏃💨` temp folder\n\n## Key Paths\n\n| Purpose | Windows Path |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Output folder** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป AiFace\\` |\n| **Tool root** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-aiface\\` |\n| **Python script** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-aiface\\gpt_aiface_image.py` |\n| **Runtime temp** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-aiface\\runtime 🏃💨\\` |\n| **Chrome CDP** | `http://127.0.0.1:9223` |\n| **GPT URL** | `https://chatgpt.com/g/g-699b39eeedc4819180aeb6ad24c464d9` |\n\n## Verification Gates\n\n### Technical Gate\n- URL must contain `backend-api/estuary/content` (real ChatGPT image)\n- Content-type must be `image/*`\n- Resolution >= 1000x700 (or >= 400x400 with `--allow-preview`)\n- File size >= 300KB (or >= 80KB with `--allow-preview`)\n\n### Vision Gate\n- Moondream describes the image\n- qwen2.5:3b judges if caption matches the prompt\n- Confidence must be >= 0.75 (adjustable with `--min-confidence`)\n- Even if vision fails, image is saved for review\n\n## Notes\n\n- No real keyboard/mouse — all via CDP/DOM only\n- Runtime temp folder is auto-deleted after completion\n- Rejects thumbnails, previews, avatars automatically\n- Only ChatGPT estuary content URLs are accepted\n\n## ⚠️ /aiface Safety Gate\n\nPer unified rules from Hermes SOUL.md:\n- ทุกครั้งที่กด `/aiface` หรือสั่งสร้างรูปหน้าคน → หยุดถามเจ้านายก่อนเสมอว่า \"อยากได้ตัวละครอะไร?\"\n- ห้ามคิดชื่อตัวละครเองหรือรัน Batch โดยพลการเด็ดขาด","path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-aiface/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":124,"output":1057,"cacheRead":101056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778233115445,"responseId":"064ce21d223c8a19e3153e2a9eeadf02"}}
