{"type":"message","id":"8ebc1456","parentId":"9a640953","timestamp":"2026-05-08T10:39:28.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So Hermes 3 (Local) couldn't find GPU info or plant info. Let me check the memory files and see if there's plant info. Also I need to count the lines in the test message.\n\nTest message: \"นี่คือคำสั่งเทสสั้นๆ: 1. ให้มึงสรุปสเปกเครื่องกู (Apinan) มาสั้นๆ 3 ข้อ 2. มึงเห็น GPU 4060 Ti ในเครื่องกูไหม? 3. บอกชื่อต้นไม้ที่กูปลูกมา 1 ชื่อ\"\n\nThis is about 3 lines if we count by numbered items. But by actual newlines in the message text... let me count: \"นี่คือคำสั่งเทสสั้นๆ:\\n1. ให้มึงสรุปสเปกเครื่องกู (Apinan) มาสั้นๆ 3 ข้อ\\n2. มึงเห็น GPU 4060 Ti ในเครื่องกูไหม?\\n3. บอกชื่อต้นไม้ที่กูปลูกมา 1 ชื่อ\"\n\nThat's 4 lines (including the first line and 3 numbered items). Or maybe 3 lines if we don't count the first line as a numbered item. Either way it's ≤10 lines so I should use the ≤10 rule: Local summarizes + tool suggestion → Cloud cross-check.\n \nNow I'm looking through the workspace memory files to find information about plants or trees that Apinan might have planted.\n","thinkingSignature":"213331af4927a246f4f70a87e804feeefd26d4ecc655f3b14b82b8b23a68decb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uu1ctm7rx574_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ -type f -name \"*.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -10","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uu1ctm7rx574_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"ต้นไม้ plant tree สวน"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":843,"output":520,"cacheRead":108096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778236747912,"responseId":"064cf04f26af93652d793496ec06f5a6"}}
