{"type":"message","id":"8b78dfaa","parentId":"dc35a14f","timestamp":"2026-05-08T13:31:21.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the CLI entry point to use the new result format and test the complete pipeline with \"เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\":","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Now test full 8-step pipeline:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_64j9rrpk","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/scripts && python3 -c \"\nfrom universal_bridge import UniversalAgentBridge\n\nbridge = UniversalAgentBridge()\nresult = bridge.run('เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU', verbose=True)\n\nprint()\nprint('='*60)\nprint('📋 FINAL REPORT')\nprint('='*60)\nprint(f'Step 1-2 INPUT: {result[\\\"step1_input\\\"]}')\nprint(f'Step 3 TRANSLATE: {result[\\\"step3_english\\\"]}')\nprint(f'Step 4-5 CLOUD: {\\\"✅\\\" if result[\\\"step4_cloud_sent\\\"] else \\\"⚠️ FILE_MODE\\\"}')\nprint(f'Step 6 EXECUTE: {result[\\\"step6_execution\\\"][\\\"commands_run\\\"]} cmds run')\nprint(f'Step 7 SUMMARY: {result[\\\"step7_summary\\\"]}')\nprint(f'Step 8 CLEANUP: {\\\"✅\\\" if result[\\\"step8_cleanup\\\"] else \\\"❌\\\"}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama-pay","model":"deepseek-v4-pro:cloud","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778247048917,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1778247077073"}}
{"type":"message","id":"899c58ba","parentId":"8b78dfaa","timestamp":"2026-05-08T13:31:21.977Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_64j9rrpk","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Step 1-2] INPUT: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU...\n[Step 3] FORCE TRANSLATE: Check CPU and GPU temperature.\n[Step 4-5] CLOUD: ✅ Cloud ตอบ\n[Step 6] EXECUTE: [] commands, success=False\n[Step 7] SUMMARIZE: [สรุป] ไม่มีผลลัพธ์จากการรันคำสั่งสำหรับ: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\n[Step 8] CLEANUP ✅ Zero Footprint\n\n============================================================\n📋 FINAL REPORT\n============================================================\nStep 1-2 INPUT: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\nStep 3 TRANSLATE: Check CPU and GPU temperature.\nStep 4-5 CLOUD: ✅\nStep 6 EXECUTE: [] cmds run\nStep 7 SUMMARY: [สรุป] ไม่มีผลลัพธ์จากการรันคำสั่งสำหรับ: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\nStep 8 CLEANUP: ✅"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":763,"aggregated":"[Step 1-2] INPUT: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU...\n[Step 3] FORCE TRANSLATE: Check CPU and GPU temperature.\n[Step 4-5] CLOUD: ✅ Cloud ตอบ\n[Step 6] EXECUTE: [] commands, success=False\n[Step 7] SUMMARIZE: [สรุป] ไม่มีผลลัพธ์จากการรันคำสั่งสำหรับ: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\n[Step 8] CLEANUP ✅ Zero Footprint\n\n============================================================\n📋 FINAL REPORT\n============================================================\nStep 1-2 INPUT: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\nStep 3 TRANSLATE: Check CPU and GPU temperature.\nStep 4-5 CLOUD: ✅\nStep 6 EXECUTE: [] cmds run\nStep 7 SUMMARY: [สรุป] ไม่มีผลลัพธ์จากการรันคำสั่งสำหรับ: เช็คอุณหภูมิ CPU และ GPU\nStep 8 CLEANUP: ✅","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778247081977}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba573f98","parentId":"899c58ba","timestamp":"2026-05-08T13:32:05.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 8-step pipeline all ran, but Step 6 (execution) found 0 commands from the cloud response. The cloud (MiniMax) probably just gave a text response without shell commands. Let me improve the command extraction to be smarter — when the cloud doesn't give explicit shell commands, we should auto-generate the appropriate commands based on the user request.\n\nLet me update the execute method to be smarter: if no commands found from cloud response, let the local LLM decide what command to run.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Steps 1-5 และ 8 ทำงานแล้ว แต่ Step 6 ไม่เจอ command — ปรับ executor ให้ฉลาดขึ้น:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7qw1g4d2","name":"filesystem__edit_file","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def execute(self, cloud_response: str, original_prompt: str = \"\", timeout: int = 30) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        รัน shell commands จริงในเครื่อง — Step 6\n        ถ้า cloud ไม่ให้ command → Local LLM เลือกให้\n        \"\"\"\n        commands = self.extract_shell_commands(cloud_response)\n        \n        # ถ้าไม่มี command จาก cloud → ให้ Local LLM หาให้\n        if not commands:\n            commands = self._smart_command(original_prompt)\n        \n        if not commands:\n            return {\"commands_run\": 0, \"outputs\": [], \"success\": False, \"error\": \"No executable commands found\"}\n        \n        results = []\n        for cmd in commands:\n            try:\n                output = subprocess.check_output(\n                    cmd, shell=True, stderr=subprocess.STDOUT,\n                    timeout=timeout, text=True\n                ).strip()\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": output, \"ok\": True})\n            except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": \"TIMEOUT\", \"ok\": False})\n            except subprocess.CalledProcessError as e:\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": (e.output or str(e)).strip(), \"ok\": False})\n            except Exception as e:\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": str(e), \"ok\": False})\n        \n        all_ok = all(r[\"ok\"] for r in results)\n        return {\n            \"commands_run\": len(results),\n            \"outputs\": results,\n            \"success\": all_ok,\n            \"raw\": \"\\n\".join(f\"$ {r['command']}\\n{r['output']}\" for r in results)\n        }\n    \n    def _smart_command(self, prompt: str) -> list[str]:\n        \"\"\"Local LLM สร้าง shell command จาก prompt\"\"\"\n        if not prompt:\n            return []\n        \n        gen_prompt = f\"\"\"Given this user request: \"{prompt}\"\n\nWhat is the SINGLE most appropriate Linux shell command to fulfill it?\nReply with ONLY the command, nothing else. No markdown, no explanation.\n\nIf temperature/temp: use 'sensors' or 'cat /sys/class/thermal/thermal_zone*/temp'\nIf RAM/memory: use 'free -h'\nIf disk: use 'df -h'\nIf CPU info: use 'cat /proc/cpuinfo | head'\nIf GPU: use 'nvidia-smi'\"\"\"\n        \n        try:\n            cmd = call_llm(\n                self.local[\"base_url\"],\n                self.local[\"model\"],\n                gen_prompt,\n                api_key=self.local[\"api_key\"],\n                system=\"You generate shell commands. Reply with the command only.\",\n                timeout=30\n            ).strip()\n            # Clean up\n            cmd = cmd.replace(\"`\", \"\").replace(\"```\", \"\").strip()\n            return [cmd] if cmd else []\n        except Exception:\n            return []","oldText":"    def execute(self, cloud_response: str, timeout: int = 30) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        รัน shell commands จริงในเครื่อง — Step 6\n        Returns: {commands_run, outputs, success}\n        \"\"\"\n        commands = self.extract_shell_commands(cloud_response)\n        if not commands:\n            return {\"commands_run\": [], \"outputs\": [], \"success\": False, \"error\": \"No executable commands found\"}\n        \n        results = []\n        for cmd in commands:\n            try:\n                output = subprocess.check_output(\n                    cmd, shell=True, stderr=subprocess.STDOUT,\n                    timeout=timeout, text=True\n                ).strip()\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": output, \"ok\": True})\n            except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": \"TIMEOUT\", \"ok\": False})\n            except subprocess.CalledProcessError as e:\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": e.output or str(e), \"ok\": False})\n            except Exception as e:\n                results.append({\"command\": cmd, \"output\": str(e), \"ok\": False})\n        \n        all_ok = all(r[\"ok\"] for r in results)\n        return {\n            \"commands_run\": len(results),\n            \"outputs\": results,\n            \"success\": all_ok,\n            \"raw\": \"\\n\".join(f\"$ {r['command']}\\n{r['output']}\" for r in results)\n        }"}],"path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/universal_bridge.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama-pay","model":"deepseek-v4-pro:cloud","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778247081983,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1778247102328"}}
