{"type":"message","id":"daf6d342","parentId":"12244c96","timestamp":"2026-05-08T14:29:44.677Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear now: the architect keeps putting `~/work/` in the plan even though it doesn't exist. The actual workspace is `~/.openclaw/workspace`. The problem is the Architect (MiniMax) is generating commands with wrong paths.\n\nI need to fix the path resolution. Currently my `_resolve_path` function in `_exec_mcp_filesystem` only resolves relative paths for MCP calls, but it doesn't fix the shell commands that the Architect generates.\n\nLet me add a path replacement step in `_exec_shell` to replace known bad paths with the correct workspace path.\n","thinkingSignature":"aaec2eb708a3f3317263002a310a95d675a42c96afec2e13007355e0774e3072"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4jr1wbpvg5ei_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/universal_bridge.py') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Fix _exec_shell to replace bad paths\nold_shell = '''    def _exec_shell(self, cmd: str) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"Run a shell command with WSL path fixes\"\"\"\n        exec_timeout = self.cfg.get(\"exec_timeout\", 45)\n\n        # Expand ~ in commands to workspace\n        cmd = os.path.expanduser(cmd)'''\n\nnew_shell = '''    def _exec_shell(self, cmd: str) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"Run a shell command with WSL path fixes\"\"\"\n        exec_timeout = self.cfg.get(\"exec_timeout\", 45)\n\n        # Expand ~ in commands\n        cmd = os.path.expanduser(cmd)\n\n        # Fix known wrong paths - Architect keeps generating ~/work which doesn't exist\n        # Map bad paths to correct workspace\n        path_fixes = {\n            '/home/apinan/work': '/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace',\n            '/home/apinan/work/': '/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace',\n            '~/work/': '/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/',\n            '~/work': '/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace',\n            '/path/to/your/folder': '/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace',\n            '/path/to/your': '/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace',\n        }\n        for wrong, right in path_fixes.items():\n            if wrong in cmd:\n                cmd = cmd.replace(wrong, right)\n                break'''\n\nif old_shell in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_shell, new_shell)\n    print(\"✅ Fixed path replacement in _exec_shell\")\nelse:\n    print(\"⚠️  Pattern not found\")\n\nwith open('/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/universal_bridge.py', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":684,"output":555,"cacheRead":81792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778250562656,"responseId":"064d264400e603d2414f0c1430d19219"}}
