{"type":"message","id":"e09586da","parentId":"229c9246","timestamp":"2026-05-08T14:37:09.110Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss wants me to restructure the 4-unit bridge with specific model names and VRAM-efficient settings. Let me:\n\n1. Load SocratiCode first (per rules)\n2. Check what models are available locally\n3. Restructure the bridge with the specified models\n4. Test with the query about old download files\n\nLet me check local Ollama models first to know what's available.\n","thinkingSignature":"ca9a5f38c8da93f3fb62d5d08205604b63a563b6980828d321be4e387e0277f8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 รับทำเลยเจ้านาย! ก่อนอื่นเช็คโมเดลที่มีในระบบก่อน:\n\n**ลำดับการใช้ MCP:**\n1. `ollama__list` → เช็คโมเดลที่มี\n2. `write` → ปรับโครงสร้างใหม่ทั้งหมด\n3. `exec` → syntax check + รันเทส\n\nกำลังทำงานอยู่ครับเจ้านาย... 🧑🏼‍💻\n\n**ลำดับ MCP:**\n1. `ollama__list` — เช็คโมเดลที่มี\n2. แก้ไฟล์ `universal_bridge.py` — ใส่โมเดลที่เจ้านายกำหนด + VRAM mode + trace ชื่อโมเดล\n3. Syntax check → รันเทส\n\nเริ่มเลย:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3m9m6nc6oxst_1","name":"ollama__list","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15364,"output":391,"cacheRead":72384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88139,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778251009698,"responseId":"064d2804e05abea6a6039a2ba02a824f"}}
